## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped
- `scripts/release.sh` — finds latest tag, auto-increments version, creates annotated tag, pushes to trigger the release workflow
- Usage: `./scripts/release.sh` (patch), `./scripts/release.sh minor`, `./scripts/release.sh major`, or `./scripts/release.sh v0.3.0-beta.1`
- Validates: must be on main, working directory clean, confirms before pushing
- Token fallback in CI workflows: uses ENGINE_ACCESS_TOKEN if set, falls back to github.token
